channel.title: Comments on: Corona Geek #75 – Super Meter, Code Snippets, and The Belly App

item.title: By: Mo
item.dc:creator: Mo
item.description:
LOL, thanks for the shout out Jen! GREAT app! I can really see the app used for so many other applications where you can teach people about different subjects using videos like you do in the Belly Dancing app. You could even sell the app for people to re-skin them for their needs.
Good luck with it.
Cheers.
Mo
